{% doc %}
  @prompt
    布局要求：
    左侧一张大图，右侧两张图片（上下排列），左右宽度比例为 942:464，整体对齐整齐，有间距。
    
    功能要求：
    - 每张图片都可以设置点击链接（整张图可点击）
    - 图片上可以添加内容：
      - 标题
      - 描述
      - 按钮（如“Shop Now”）
      - 按钮链接
    - 内容显示在图片内部（支持居中或左下角）
    
    响应式要求：
    - PC端保持当前布局
    - 移动端改为上下排列（3张图竖排）
    
    性能要求（重点）：
    - 代码结构尽量简洁，避免冗余
    - 不引入额外JS或第三方库
    - 优化图片加载（使用懒加载等）
    - 避免布局偏移（CLS问题）
    - 不影响页面加载速度
    
    技术要求：
    - 使用 Liquid + HTML + CSS
    - 兼容 Dawn 主题
    - 不影响原主题样式
    , 桌面宽度控制单位为px。图片上的内容中心改为顶部居中，另外增加一个左上角的方式。可以单独设置标题，描述的字体颜色。增加控制按钮的圆角半径。, 整个模块默认居中，并且图片之间的间隔小一点。按钮的内部上下边距小一点。, 整个模块两侧空白的电脑端边距为50px，手机端为15px, 图片的格式改成填满, 镞左侧内容和右侧内容比例为2.03 : 1, 第一张图片的W:H为942：635，, 错了，不是按第一张图片比例，是整个模块的W:H为1415：635, 还需要可以设置整个模块的上下边距，另外手机为目前怎么显示不了图片，你检查下代码是否有问题, 第二张第三张图片手机端无法显示？, 移动端的内容标题，描述，购买按钮的间距小一点，每个电脑端图片对应设置一个移动端的图片上传，最后
    性能要求（重点）：
    - 代码结构尽量简洁，避免冗余
    - 不引入额外JS或第三方库
    - 优化图片加载（使用懒加载等）
    - 避免布局偏移（CLS问题）
    - 不影响页面加载速度
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-split-gallery-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_px }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.spacing_top }}px 50px {{ block.settings.spacing_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 44.88%;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
    max-height: 300px;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    {% if block.settings.content_position == 'center' %}
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      text-align: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'top-center' %}
      top: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      text-align: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'top-left' %}
      top: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
      left: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
      text-align: left;
    {% else %}
      bottom: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
      left: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
      text-align: left;
    {% endif %}
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: calc(100% - {{ block.settings.content_padding | times: 2 }}px);
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity }});
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_radius }}px;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: calc(66.89% - {{ block.settings.gap | divided_by: 2.0 }}px);
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: calc(33.11% - {{ block.settings.gap | divided_by: 2.0 }}px);
    height: 100%;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__image-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-split-gallery__image-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-split-gallery-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      padding: {{ block.settings.spacing_top }}px 15px {{ block.settings.spacing_bottom }}px;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: static;
      padding-bottom: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: {{ block.settings.gap }}px;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      padding-bottom: 67.4%;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: {{ block.settings.gap }}px;
      grid-template-rows: none;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__left-{{ ai_gen_id }} .ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__right-{{ ai_gen_id }} .ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
      height: auto;
      padding-bottom: 67.4%;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__right-{{ ai_gen_id }} .ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }} .ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.content_position == 'center' or block.settings.content_position == 'top-center' %}
        max-width: 90%;
      {% else %}
        max-width: calc(100% - 32px);
        {% if block.settings.content_position == 'top-left' %}
          top: 16px;
        {% else %}
          bottom: 16px;
        {% endif %}
        left: 16px;
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__image-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: none;
    }

    .ai-split-gallery__image-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-split-gallery-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-split-gallery__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-split-gallery__left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.image_1_link != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.image_1_link }}" class="ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% endif %}
          <div class="ai-split-gallery__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% assign desktop_image_1 = block.settings.image_1 %}
            {% assign mobile_image_1 = block.settings.image_1_mobile %}
            {% if mobile_image_1 == blank %}
              {% assign mobile_image_1 = desktop_image_1 %}
            {% endif %}

            {% if desktop_image_1 %}
              <img
                src="{{ desktop_image_1 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                srcset="{{ desktop_image_1 | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                        {{ desktop_image_1 | image_url: width: 900 }} 900w,
                        {{ desktop_image_1 | image_url: width: 1200 }} 1200w"
                sizes="67vw"
                alt="{{ desktop_image_1.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-split-gallery__image-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ desktop_image_1.width }}"
                height="{{ desktop_image_1.height }}"
              >
            {% endif %}

            {% if mobile_image_1 %}
              <img
                src="{{ mobile_image_1 | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                srcset="{{ mobile_image_1 | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w,
                        {{ mobile_image_1 | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                        {{ mobile_image_1 | image_url: width: 800 }} 800w"
                sizes="100vw"
                alt="{{ mobile_image_1.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-split-gallery__image-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ mobile_image_1.width }}"
                height="{{ mobile_image_1.height }}"
              >
            {% endif %}

            {% if desktop_image_1 == blank and mobile_image_1 == blank %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if block.settings.overlay_opacity > 0 %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.image_1_title != blank or block.settings.image_1_description != blank or block.settings.image_1_button_text != blank %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if block.settings.image_1_title != blank %}
                  <h3 class="ai-split-gallery__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_1_title }}</h3>
                {% endif %}
                {% if block.settings.image_1_description != blank %}
                  <p class="ai-split-gallery__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_1_description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                {% if block.settings.image_1_button_text != blank and block.settings.image_1_button_link != blank %}
                  <span class="ai-split-gallery__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_1_button_text }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% if block.settings.image_1_link != blank %}
          </a>
        {% else %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-split-gallery__right-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.image_2_link != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.image_2_link }}" class="ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% endif %}
          <div class="ai-split-gallery__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% assign desktop_image_2 = block.settings.image_2 %}
            {% assign mobile_image_2 = block.settings.image_2_mobile %}
            {% if mobile_image_2 == blank %}
              {% assign mobile_image_2 = desktop_image_2 %}
            {% endif %}

            {% if desktop_image_2 %}
              <img
                src="{{ desktop_image_2 | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                srcset="{{ desktop_image_2 | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w,
                        {{ desktop_image_2 | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w"
                sizes="33vw"
                alt="{{ desktop_image_2.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-split-gallery__image-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ desktop_image_2.width }}"
                height="{{ desktop_image_2.height }}"
              >
            {% endif %}

            {% if mobile_image_2 %}
              <img
                src="{{ mobile_image_2 | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                srcset="{{ mobile_image_2 | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w,
                        {{ mobile_image_2 | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                        {{ mobile_image_2 | image_url: width: 800 }} 800w"
                sizes="100vw"
                alt="{{ mobile_image_2.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-split-gallery__image-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ mobile_image_2.width }}"
                height="{{ mobile_image_2.height }}"
              >
            {% endif %}

            {% if desktop_image_2 == blank and mobile_image_2 == blank %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if block.settings.overlay_opacity > 0 %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.image_2_title != blank or block.settings.image_2_description != blank or block.settings.image_2_button_text != blank %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if block.settings.image_2_title != blank %}
                  <h3 class="ai-split-gallery__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_2_title }}</h3>
                {% endif %}
                {% if block.settings.image_2_description != blank %}
                  <p class="ai-split-gallery__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_2_description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                {% if block.settings.image_2_button_text != blank and block.settings.image_2_button_link != blank %}
                  <span class="ai-split-gallery__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_2_button_text }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% if block.settings.image_2_link != blank %}
          </a>
        {% else %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-split-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.image_3_link != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.image_3_link }}" class="ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-split-gallery__item-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% endif %}
          <div class="ai-split-gallery__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% assign desktop_image_3 = block.settings.image_3 %}
            {% assign mobile_image_3 = block.settings.image_3_mobile %}
            {% if mobile_image_3 == blank %}
              {% assign mobile_image_3 = desktop_image_3 %}
            {% endif %}

            {% if desktop_image_3 %}
              <img
                src="{{ desktop_image_3 | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                srcset="{{ desktop_image_3 | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w,
                        {{ desktop_image_3 | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w"
                sizes="33vw"
                alt="{{ desktop_image_3.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-split-gallery__image-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ desktop_image_3.width }}"
                height="{{ desktop_image_3.height }}"
              >
            {% endif %}

            {% if mobile_image_3 %}
              <img
                src="{{ mobile_image_3 | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                srcset="{{ mobile_image_3 | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w,
                        {{ mobile_image_3 | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                        {{ mobile_image_3 | image_url: width: 800 }} 800w"
                sizes="100vw"
                alt="{{ mobile_image_3.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-split-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-split-gallery__image-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ mobile_image_3.width }}"
                height="{{ mobile_image_3.height }}"
              >
            {% endif %}

            {% if desktop_image_3 == blank and mobile_image_3 == blank %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if block.settings.overlay_opacity > 0 %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.image_3_title != blank or block.settings.image_3_description != blank or block.settings.image_3_button_text != blank %}
              <div class="ai-split-gallery__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if block.settings.image_3_title != blank %}
                  <h3 class="ai-split-gallery__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_3_title }}</h3>
                {% endif %}
                {% if block.settings.image_3_description != blank %}
                  <p class="ai-split-gallery__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_3_description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                {% if block.settings.image_3_button_text != blank and block.settings.image_3_button_link != blank %}
                  <span class="ai-split-gallery__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.image_3_button_text }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% if block.settings.image_3_link != blank %}
          </a>
        {% else %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

